      "role": "user",
      "content": "nothing major, just the backend processing. the new model is faster but it's a bit more \"standard\" in its responses. we want the guide to basically say that while the speed is an improvement, the personal touch and deep itinerary nuance they're used to with you might feel a bit different. can you draft a few paragraphs that explain this to the VIP clients so they don't feel like they're losing the luxury experience?",
